lenders.loan_because: I love the self-sustaining model of microloans.  There are few ways as effective in developing nations as providing funds so that desiring individuals can work towards release from generational poverty.  Many other types of giving provide traditional "charity," which isn't necessarily bad.  But microfinance provides men and women the opportunity to do more than merely exist until the next charitable gift.  Microfinance is one of the few giving opportunities that actually helps bring transformation.
